{
  "stem": "16473.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 304.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I think maybe that's how my mother perceived that it's time to get me out because this is, this is happening.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Do you remember the name of the border town you were in?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, all I know it was on the border of Yugoslavia and Hungary.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, somewhere between five and six.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, that's not right either, because I went to first grade.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Somewhere between six and seven, maybe.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, I'm not good at the dates.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[INTERPOSING VOICES]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Could be.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I really think that the, the reason that I'm so unclear about dates is because I've been, I've been told to lie about my age and, and deliberately cloud over things.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And ever since then, I, I am not good with-- with dates, that they're just a sore point with me because all reality has been turned upside down.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, I'm not six, you know, I'm five, I'm not six.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm not Jewish, I'm Catholic.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So everything got sort of turned tipsy-turvy on me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I think some of that has-- has remained.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I always have to think back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Even about my own age, [LAUGHS] I have to think back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because my mother was afraid that if I went to public school there, I'd give away my Jewishness.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was very dangerous to be Jewish, as I found out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One of my most harrowing experiences was playing with the village kids.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I think it's because I was wearing something different, they started yelling at me and they started calling me Jew.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I ran like crazy, my heart was pounding.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I thought I was surely going to die because they knew who I was.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I ran, you know, to the home that I was living in.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
